These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Color: orange, grey
Beverage: milk, almond-milk
1. Beverage:milk is in an even position##4
2. Beverage:almond-milk == Color:grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Color   | grey | orange |
| Beverage     | almond-milk    | milk   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Color: apricot, yellow
Food: spinach, onion
1. Food:spinach is in an odd position##4
2. Color:yellow is on the left of Color:apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Color   | yellow | apricot        |
| Food      | spinach  | onion |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: sudoku, video-games
Cigar: dannemann, pall-mall
1. Cigar:dannemann is in an odd position##4
2. Hobby:video-games is on the left of Hobby:sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Hobby   | video-games    | sudoku |
| Cigar   | dannemann | pall-mall |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
